channel.title: ASF Jira
channel.description: This file is an XML representation of an issue

item.title: [HIVE-20744] Use SQL constraints to improve join reordering algorithm
item.description: Till now, it was all based on stats stored for the base tables and their columns. Now the optimizer can rely on constraints. Hence, this patch is for the join reordering costing to use constraints, and if it does not find any, rely on old code path.
item.summary: Use SQL constraints to improve join reordering algorithm

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.
